v. 0.2
====================================
- separate browser settings and package settings in two INI files
- browser settings file can be in the browser binary folder or in the default user settings folder
- package settings file can be supplied from command line option or in the browser binary folder
- package settings file can be in the package root folder
- DATA_ROOT can be in user's data directory
- built-in default values for browser and package settings

- better documentation for censor.pl
- security tests in separate files
- separate resource file for censor.pl

- start Perl debugger in script environment when script is inside the current package
    and in system environment when script is outside the current package
- dbgformatter.pl fatpacked together with Syntax::Highlight::Engine::Kate

- single template for all HTML error messages
- translations for all HTML error messages
- HTML error pages for missing browser settings file and missing start page
- user-supplied JS prompt when check-user-input-before-quit finds user input

- better SQLite test

v. 0.3
====================================
- internal JavaScript-based code editor - ACE;
    code editor will edit settings files too